Do’s
Do set your profiles to private to control who sees your personal life.
Do think before you post; ask if you'd be okay with a recruiter seeing it.
Do verify information from a credible source before sharing it.
Do use professional profile pictures on platforms like LinkedIn.
Do give credit to original creators when sharing their work.


Don’ts
Don't tag others in embarrassing photos without their permission.
Don't post offensive, discriminatory, or illegal content.
Don't vent about your professors, college, or workplace online.
Don't share sensitive personal data like your address or phone number.
Don't engage with trolls or participate in cyberbullying/harassment.
